   Ok, I'm going to add counters to DMDX 2.2.00.  New keywords will include:

	<brdiags> turn on branching diagnostics in .zil or .azk output
	<set N1,N2> set counter N1 to value N2
	<inc N1> increment counter N1
	<dec N1> decrement counter N1
	<brLE0 N1,N2> branch to item N2 if counter N1 less than or equal to 0
	<brGT0 N1,N2> branch to item N2 if counter N1 greater than 0

   I'm not going to be adding conditional decrements or increments as they 
are messy to implement (requiring flags to be set for tests once the RT has 
been gathered), if people need them existing branching can be combined with 
<inc> or <dec>.

-jonathan (j.c.f.)

